#: ../../R/RTFAQ.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Usenet: primarily written, by analogy with :ref:`RTFM`\\] Abbrev. for ‘Read"
" the FAQ!’, an exhortation that the person addressed ought to read the "
"newsgroup's :ref:`FAQ-list` before posting questions."
msgstr ""
"[Usenet: 主に書き言葉。\\ :ref:`RTFM`\\ との類推による] ‘Read the "
"FAQ!’の略で、相手は質問を投稿する前にニュースグループの\\ :ref:`FAQ-list`\\ を読むべきだ、という勧告。"
